Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾发生过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“极光战争”的这场战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.24,0:00:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生在赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和茵费利亚之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚便断绝交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.45,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界面临即将灭亡的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出来拯救这场危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是一群无名的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.64,0:02:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德·哈谢尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.52,0:02:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那条命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我玛萝妮·布鲁卡诺要定了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.86,0:02:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2话  海上的奖金猎人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大致上是没怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是里德保护我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了  里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  里德不见了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…  站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.64,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是里德的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把他怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了那个男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.52,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚刚和怪物的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从头到尾都在旁边看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你们这样的绊脚石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不配那个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在毫无力量的家伙身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人将无法充分发挥他的本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以还是忘了他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为里德好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少擅作主张了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.79,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德   等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.63,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有办法驯养凶猛著称的飞龙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫玛萝妮的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么来头？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据王立天文台台长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐西摩斯的调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所进言的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们茵费利亚和赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不久的将来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.58,0:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将发生相撞的大崩落一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已经有确切的答案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于赛雷斯提亚的破坏行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓决定要抗战到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  战争了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…怎么会这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做一点用也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.67,0:05:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…就只有我们自己来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我们自己的力量来收集大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走   到赛雷斯提亚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去赛雷斯提亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.56,0:05:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做梦了是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.69,0:05:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是刚刚那些都不是梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…特地向茵费利亚王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知世界即将面临的危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却遭遇莫名其妙的待遇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.17,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.17,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再暂时忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玛萝妮·布鲁卡诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是专门消灭怪物的赏金猎人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏金猎人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常需要你的本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   应该可以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看上了你的本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起你就是我的搭档了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅作主张啊你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摔下去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大概是那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾在这里露宿过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示她的目的地的线索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个看了乱不顺眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫玛萝妮来着的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在光想到她我都还一肚子气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~法拉  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我捡到了这种东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写了些什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打倒可恶的海中恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.93,0:06:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就赏赐一千万G的奖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上都市贝鲁卡纽领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上都市贝鲁卡纽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  那就是海上都市贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上都市贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.62,0:06:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以主岛贝鲁卡岛为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所构成的海上都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡岛的周遭有许多的小岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上散布了推动各种农业   商业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及手工业等等产业的设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些产业全都高度的发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少仰赖其他的都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此贝鲁卡纽这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在茵费利亚国内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也形成了他们独特的文化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.84,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到我们海上都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是贝鲁卡纽的领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是愿意替我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭海中恶魔的勇者是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海中恶魔大概是怪物之类的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.19,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还没有人看过他的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为遇到他的人们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个活着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~好美的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我们处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.14,0:07:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成功消灭海中恶魔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.01,0:07:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛连我也算在内…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先消除长途旅行的劳顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且养精蓄锐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是目前的先决条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请容许我们暂时先休息一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.82,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请两位在我这宅邸尽情的休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是活过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回你伙伴那里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能让你忘掉他们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来帮助你忘掉他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到你刚才那个表情啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡纽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我们正在找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能载我们到贝鲁卡岛的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛   最近那一带啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有怪物在出没呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个…要去贝鲁卡纽是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在正要回去贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话就搭我们的船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认我的做法是太强硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那个啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重视伙伴的那种情义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一瞬间我就非常明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重视伙伴的情义？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你明明可以闪开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你是故意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他们的挡箭牌对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你也有手下留情不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…从你们离开茵费利亚城后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直跟在你们后面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.99,0:10:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我放弃找你当我的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这一次的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你务必要帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.24,0:10:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要忙着赶路耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.84,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.21,0:10:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想…保护这个岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾在这岛上发生过什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了钱而已！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那个原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然还有什么原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.86,0:10:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我也在领主面前已经讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你就帮我一次忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧  伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说这些废话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又是海中恶魔干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧  普拉提亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.00,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人要买饭盒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一样这么努力工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜妮玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  包在我们身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.98,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个海中恶魔就交给我们对付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  不找里德了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德的事固然让人担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是看到大家有困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.69,0:13:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能够置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   搞不好打倒怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是个不错的战略呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那个叫玛萝妮的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也想干掉那个怪物才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们出面打倒怪物的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他也一定会现身的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.97,0:13:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到里德之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民们也能从此脱困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一箭双鵰的好战略呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯行得通行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的女孩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打哪里来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是伊库利亚啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是法拉他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.06,0:13:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便前往传说中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海中恶魔栖息的海域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算要把他给引出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了   都准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   我们事先预测一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫海中恶魔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么样的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么做能引出怪物吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.79,0:14:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都还没调查完呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只要打倒他就行了不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点   召唤大晶灵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾水之医治来保护汝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特  西尔夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾之炙热魔掌熔化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空之风啊   降下来并化为龙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位全看你们了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我们身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是想这么说不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次好像也是水属性的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我似乎是帮不上什么忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就看我的   温蒂妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种小角色的怪物  凭我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌不过的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不用太指望…   喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腾空板！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好   来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海中恶魔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.95,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心前面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.96,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特  西尔夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钉暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.81,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还不能确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  那家伙朝岛的方向去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海中恶魔朝我们这边冲过来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  这里非常危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点去避难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许犯了非常严重的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的真正面目是海豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.98,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹只要受到了一次攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶猛度就会更剧烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是随便乱攻击的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会让危害更加扩大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面是这样记载的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠一次的攻击打倒他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去  小镇会有危险的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  你说该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔你看那个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了   是里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我说的步骤同时攻击知道吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.00,0:17:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.75,0:17:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.98,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德他赢了耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.08,0:17:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你回来  里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫法拉对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想救人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先秤秤看自己有几两重再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不管经过了多少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远都是只说不做的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说不做的女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是只说不做的女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的伙伴将会来晋见您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候请把其馀的部份交给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…就此告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.60,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样里德…
